      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with six individual throttle bodies and double VANOS variable valve timing. This specimen boasts a crisp Getrag six-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The chassis is structurally flawless, with no subframe fatigue, and the suspension retains its original geometry for telepathic turn-in. Finished in original paint with zero oxidation, the interior features pristine Nappa leather with no bolster wear and a crystal-clear instrument cluster. This is an investment-grade, longitudinal RWD masterpiece for the true driving purist.",
