      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom-quality condition, having been meticulously stored in a climate-controlled garage since its initial purchase. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like luster with a professional ceramic coating that highlights the flawless bodywork\u2014not a single stone chip, swirl mark, or door ding is present. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the premium Nappa leather upholstery remains supple and retains its original factory scent, with absolutely zero wear on the bolsters or touchpoints. Every electronic feature, from the immersive surround-sound system to the advanced driver-assistance suite, functions with precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having followed a rigorous maintenance schedule exclusively at authorized service centers. The engine bay is immaculate, and the undercarriage reflects the same level of care as the visible surfaces. Included are all original keys, a complete set of stamped service records, and the original window sticker. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to acquire a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line.",
